Original.CommandText:
SELECT *
FROM GIM.dbo.CLIENT
LEFT OUTER JOIN GIM.dbo.CLIENT_TRANSACTION ON GIM.dbo.CLIENT.CLIENT_ID = GIM.dbo.CLIENT_TRANSACTION.CLIENT_ID
INNER JOIN GIM.dbo.BROKER ON GIM.dbo.BROKER.BROKER_ID = GIM.dbo.CLIENT_TRANSACTION.BROKER_ID
WHERE GIM.dbo.CLIENT.CLIENT_CITY = 'GEORGETOWN'
  AND GIM.dbo.BROKER.BROKER_FIRST_NAME LIKE 'D%'

SELECT *
FROM GIM.dbo.CLIENT cl,
     GIM.dbo.CLIENT_TRANSACTION ct,
     GIM.dbo.BROKER b
WHERE NOT EXISTS
    (SELECT NULL
     FROM GIM.dbo.CLIENT_TRANSACTION E2
     WHERE E2.INVESTMENT_ID IN
         (SELECT i.INVESTMENT_ID
          FROM GIM.dbo.INVESTMENT i,
               GIM.dbo.INVESTMENT_TYPE it
          WHERE it.INVESTMENT_TYPE_NAME = 'COMMON STOCK')
       AND SUBSTRING (E2.ACTION,
                      1,
                      4) = 'SELL'
       AND cl.CLIENT_CITY = 'GEORGETOWN'
       AND b.BROKER_ID = E2.BROKER_ID)
  AND cl.BROKER_ID = b.BROKER_ID
  AND ct.BROKER_ID = b.BROKER_ID
  AND ct.CLIENT_ID = cl.CLIENT_ID
  AND b.BROKER_ID IS NOT NULL;

Original.CommandText:
SELECT
    BROKER.BROKER_ID,
    BROKER.BROKER_LAST_NAME,
    BROKER.BROKER_MIDDLE_INITIAL,
    CLIENT.BROKER_ID,
    CLIENT.CLIENT_CITY,
    CLIENT.CLIENT_LAST_NAME
FROM
    GIM.dbo.BROKER,
    GIM.dbo.CLIENT,
    GIM.dbo.CLIENT_TRANSACTION
WHERE
    CLIENT.CLIENT_FIRST_NAME IN (SELECT B.CLIENT_FIRST_NAME
                                 FROM
                                     GIM.dbo.CLIENT_TRANSACTION A,
                                     GIM.dbo.CLIENT B
                                 WHERE
                                     B.CLIENT_ID = A.CLIENT_ID AND
                                     A.ACTION = 'BUY' AND
                                     A.CLIENT_TRANSACTION_ID IN (SELECT E1.CLIENT_TRANSACTION_ID
                                                                 FROM GIM.dbo.CLIENT_TRANSACTION E1
                                                                 WHERE
                                                                     PRICE > (SELECT AVG (PRICE)
                                                                              FROM
                                                                                  GIM.dbo.CLIENT_TRANSACTION E2,
                                                                                  GIM.dbo.BROKER D1
                                                                              WHERE
                                                                                  E1.BROKER_ID = E2.BROKER_ID AND
                                                                                  E2.BROKER_ID = D1.BROKER_ID AND
                                                                                  EXISTS (SELECT 1
                                                                                          FROM GIM.dbo.OFFICE_LOCATION L1
                                                                                          WHERE L1.OFFICE_LOCATION_ID = D1.
                                                                                                  OFFICE_LOCATION_ID)) AND
                                                                     E1.NUMBER_OF_UNITS > 1)
                                 GROUP BY
                                     B.CLIENT_FIRST_NAME,
                                     B.CLIENT_LAST_NAME) AND
    GIM.dbo.CLIENT.BROKER_ID = GIM.dbo.BROKER.BROKER_ID AND
    GIM.dbo.CLIENT_TRANSACTION.BROKER_ID = GIM.dbo.BROKER.BROKER_ID AND
    GIM.dbo.CLIENT_TRANSACTION.CLIENT_ID = GIM.dbo.CLIENT.CLIENT_ID
GROUP BY
    BROKER.BROKER_ID,
    BROKER.BROKER_LAST_NAME,
    BROKER.BROKER_MIDDLE_INITIAL,
    CLIENT.BROKER_ID,
    CLIENT.CLIENT_CITY,
    CLIENT.CLIENT_LAST_NAME
ORDER BY BROKER.BROKER_ID

SELECT *
FROM
    GIM.CLIENT C,
    GIM.CLIENT_TRANSACTION T,
    GIM.BROKER B
WHERE
    C.CLIENT_ID(+) = T.CLIENT_ID AND
    T.BROKER_ID = B.BROKER_ID AND
    C.CLIENT_CITY = 'GEORGETOWN' AND
    B.BROKER_FIRST_NAME LIKE 'D%'

FROM
    GIM.CLIENT cl,
    GIM.CLIENT_TRANSACTION ct,
    GIM.BROKER b
WHERE

                FROM GIM.CLIENT_TRANSACTION E2
                WHERE
                    E2.INVESTMENT_ID IN (SELECT i.INVESTMENT_ID
                                         FROM
